      {
        "end": 4.701,
        "index": 1,
        "start": 2.2,
        "text": "Welcome to Cascade of Effects."
      },
      {
        "end": 16.203,
        "index": 2,
        "start": 4.701,
        "text": "These are stories about failures people think they already understand: Challenger, Therac-25, Hyatt Regency, Semmelweis, Tacoma Narrows, Piltdown Man, 737 MAX, and Titanic."
      },
      {
        "end": 26.706,
        "index": 3,
        "start": 16.203,
        "text": "Each episode follows the same question: what changed, who missed it, and how did the system turn that blindness into consequence?"
      },
      {
        "end": 30.707,
        "index": 4,
        "start": 26.706,
        "text": "The pattern is never a single bad decision."
      },
      {
        "end": 37.209,
        "index": 5,
        "start": 30.707,
        "text": "It is a chain of assumptions that stays respectable after reality has moved."
      },
      {
        "end": 42.71,
        "index": 6,
        "start": 37.209,
        "text": "The headline is only the doorway. The mechanism is the story."
      }
    ],
